---
import WireframeLayout from '../../layouts/WireframeLayout.astro';
---

<WireframeLayout title="France Travel">
  <header>
    <nav class="main-nav">
      <a href="/" class="logo">Chez Sargaux</a>
      <a href="/france" class="back-link">← Back to France</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <h1>Travel</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Getting to Village De Sully</p>

    <section class="travel-grid">
      <div class="content-box">
        <h3>Getting There</h3>
        <p><strong>By Air</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Paris CDG</strong> — [Distance, ~Xh by car/train]</li>
          <li><strong>Paris Orly</strong> — [Distance]</li>
          <li><strong>Lyon</strong> — [Distance, may be closer?]</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="note"><em>Research needed: Best airport for the venue location</em></p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-box">
        <h3>By Train</h3>
        <p>TGV from Paris to [nearest station]</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>[Station Name]</strong> — [Distance from venue]</li>
          <li>Trains run [frequency]</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="note"><em>Decision: Arrange group transport from station?</em></p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-box">
        <h3>By Car</h3>
        <p>From Paris: [Xh drive via A6/etc.]</p>
        <p>Parking available at the village</p>
        <p class="note">Rental car recommended if exploring the region</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-box">
        <h3>Shuttle Service</h3>
        <p><em>Decision: Provide group transport?</em></p>
        <ul>
          <li>From Paris on Friday?</li>
          <li>From nearest train station?</li>
          <li>Back to Paris/station on Sunday?</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="note">Let us know your travel plans in the RSVP</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-box">
        <h3>Extending Your Trip</h3>
        <p>If you're coming from abroad, consider:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Burgundy wine region</strong> — Famous vineyards nearby</li>
          <li><strong>Dijon</strong> — [Distance], historic city</li>
          <li><strong>Lyon</strong> — [Distance], food capital of France</li>
          <li><strong>Paris</strong> — Before or after the weekend</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-box">
        <h3>Practical Info</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Currency:</strong> Euro (€)</li>
          <li><strong>Language:</strong> French (English widely understood)</li>
          <li><strong>Timezone:</strong> CET (UTC+1) / CEST in May (UTC+2)</li>
          <li><strong>Weather in late May:</strong> [Typical conditions]</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Sam Gross</p>
  </footer>
</WireframeLayout>

<style>
  header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  .main-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .logo {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .back-link {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #666;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  main {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .travel-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content-box p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .content-box ul {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content-box li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .content-box em {
    color: #f59e0b;
  }

  .note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #888;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  footer {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  footer p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #888;
  }
</style>
